Invocation Name: bank on l. a.
des:
Bank on L.A. (Bank on Los Angeles) is a city-wide campaign to educate communities about banking and financial education. The initiative is spearheaded by RISE Financial Pathways (risela.org) and other local banking & community partners. 

For more information about Bank on L.A. please visit risela.org.
